title: Kelsey Smith // 192
description:
In 2007, an 18-year-old woman headed to Target to buy her boyfriend an anniversary present. But when she didn’t return home that evening, her family joined police in the search for her and her car. When crucial surveillance footage was uncovered the following day, it showed someone stalking and abducting her. This is the story of Kelsey Smith.
